<img border="0" src="pics/executivegames/RevAProtoBoard2.jpg" width="250" height="108"></a><br>
</font><font size="2" face="Arial">
Left and right: Unique Rev A prototype board.<br>
The white arrows and circles show some of Glen's fixes.<br>
<br>
