<a href="pics/executivegames/faceoff_unit_rev_c.jpg">
<img src="pics/executivegames/faceoff_unit_rev_c.jpg" width="250" height="92" border="0"></a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<a href="pics/executivegames/faceoff_unit_rev_e1.jpg">
<img src="pics/executivegames/faceoff_unit_rev_e1.jpg" width="250" height="93" border="0"></a><br>
<font size="2">Face-Off units, Rev. C (left) and Rev. E1 (right). Note the different center labels,<br>
and the different depth of the scoring area due to the way the LED displays are 
mounted.<br><br><br>
</font>
